product_name: Timberland Earthkeeper Front Country Oxford Shoes - Men's
long_description: With a hand-sewn look and soft nubuck leather, the Timberland Earthkeeper(R) Front Country Oxford Shoes deliver all-day style and comfort on your casual, warm-weather excursions. Classic hand-sewn styling is applied to the nubuck leather uppers for a great look. Nubuck leather uppers feature leather from a tannery highly rated for its water, energy and waste-management practices by a third-party environmental audit. Elastic laces allow easy on and off. Extra-soft linings and footbeds are made from 100% recycled PET plastic. Anti-fatigue removable footbeds provide exceptional standing comfort, shock absorption and energy return all day long. Timberland Earthkeeper(R) Front Country Oxford Shoes have durable Green Rubber(TM) cupsoles for traction; soles are made from 42% recycled rubber.
